{"event": "dialogue", "npc": "locandiere di Greyhollow", "speaker": "greyhollow_innkeeper", "text": "(He looks up from polishing a mug that appears to have been polished fifty times already.) Welcome to the Hollow Hearth. Food, drink, a bed, or gossip? I'm stocked in all four.", "choices": [{"index": 0, "text": "I'd like to see what you're selling."}, {"index": 1, "text": "I need a room for the night."}, {"index": 2, "text": "What do you know about Greyhollow?"}, {"index": 3, "text": "Any rumors worth hearing?"}, {"index": 4, "text": "What do you know about the Thornpillar dimming?"}, {"index": 5, "text": "Just passing through."}]}
{"event": "dialogue_choice", "npc": "locandiere di Greyhollow", "selected": {"index": 3, "text": "Any rumors worth hearing?"}}
{"event": "dialogue", "npc": "locandiere di Greyhollow", "speaker": "greyhollow_innkeeper", "text": "(Leans on the bar conspiratorially.) Cost you five gold. Worth every piece.", "choices": [{"index": 0, "text": "Pay for a rumor. (5 gold)"}, {"index": 1, "text": "Not today."}]}
{"event": "dialogue_choice", "npc": "locandiere di Greyhollow", "selected": {"index": 0, "text": "Pay for a rumor. (5 gold)"}}
{"event": "dialogue", "npc": "locandiere di Greyhollow", "speaker": "greyhollow_innkeeper", "text": "(Drops his voice.) Three nights ago, a Concordat trader came through. Staying the night, nervous as a cat. Before he left he told me he'd heard that High Consul Osel's brother — the one who disappeared six years ago after some scandal — was seen near the Underlurk Chasm access. A Concordat official, in cult territory. If that's true, someone important has some very embarrassing connections.", "choices": [{"index": 0, "text": "Osel's brother. I'll keep that in mind."}]}
{"event": "dialogue_choice", "npc": "locandiere di Greyhollow", "selected": {"index": 0, "text": "Osel's brother. I'll keep that in mind."}}
